        public static final java.lang.String JSON_STATUS

        • cancelled
        • error

      • JSON_ELAPSED_TIME

        public static final java.lang.String JSON_ELAPSED_TIME
        The elapsed time in ms from the point the job started. If the job is finished, this is the duration it took to process the job. Part of the getStatus(String, javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest, javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse) response.
